  "2324150": {
    "name": "Neuroshima Hex",
    "steam_appid": 2324150,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2324150/extras/a06d97ed273b3dded620780c66a361ca.poster.avif?t=1770800965\" width=614 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2324150/extras/a06d97ed273b3dded620780c66a361ca.webm?t=1770800965\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2324150/extras/a06d97ed273b3dded620780c66a361ca.mp4?t=1770800965\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>神经岛六角战棋</strong> 是一款基于畅销桌游、拥有独特宇宙观的<strong>回合制策略游戏</strong>，获得了全球玩家的认可。现在，首次以完整数字版形式登陆PC平台——<i>包含单人模式、本地多人游戏及在线PvP</i>。<br><br>化身为其中一个派系的指挥官，与其他军队对决——包括传说中的<i>莫洛克</i>，一群反抗人类的自动化机器网络。每场游戏都是一场快节奏、紧张激烈的战斗，考验你的战术、计划和预测对手动作的能力。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2324150/extras/b6f612234750259cb49370a21e5cda9a.poster.avif?t=1770800965\" width=614 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2324150/extras/b6f612234750259cb49370a21e5cda9a.webm?t=1770800965\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2324150/extras/b6f612234750259cb49370a21e5cda9a.mp4?t=1770800965\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>扮演独特军队的领袖，带领你的部队走向胜利。战斗的原因？经典题材：水、燃料、武器、生存——这些都是锈迹、尘土和毒素笼罩世界中最宝贵的资源。<br><br>游戏机制基于在六边形棋盘上战略性地放置单位和模块的棋子。选择、组合、部署并激活——<strong>每一个决定都至关重要</strong>。这是一款<strong>节奏快速</strong>，但<strong>智力要求高的回合制游戏</strong>，良好的计划至关重要。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2324150/extras/0caac419628dac5e915fdae816d573ee.poster.avif?t=1770800965\" width=614 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2324150/extras/0caac419628dac5e915fdae816d573ee.webm?t=1770800965\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2324150/extras/0caac419628dac5e915fdae816d573ee.mp4?t=1770800965\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>起步时你将拥有多达<strong>10支风格迥异的军队</strong>，各自拥有独特的游戏风格、强弱点和特殊机制。每个派系提供不同的战术选择——从强力的正面攻击到精准的反击与机械陷阱。<br><br>基础版本中的可用军队包括：<strong>莫洛克、霸权、博尔格、哨所、钢铁警察、斯玛特、维加斯、纽约、野兽以及密西西比</strong>。<br><br>此外，作为<strong>DLC</strong>，我们增加了<strong>3支军队：新丛林、沙拉什、乌拉诺波利斯</strong>。<br><br>未来我们计划<strong>继续添加桌游版本中的更多扩展内容</strong>。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2324150/extras/ca5440c7bd0e4548f878482d4b73383e.poster.avif?t=1770800965\" width=614 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2324150/extras/ca5440c7bd0e4548f878482d4b73383e.webm?t=1770800965\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2324150/extras/ca5440c7bd0e4548f878482d4b73383e.mp4?t=1770800965\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>无论你是为了放松还是参与比赛模式，总能找到适合你的玩法。<br><br>游戏特色包括：<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>丰富的单人AI模式<br></li><li>带有<strong>剧情</strong>的战役模式<br></li><li><strong>本地多人游戏</strong>（同一台电脑）<br></li><li><strong>在线PvP对战</strong></li></ul><br>这使得神经岛六角战棋既适合家庭休闲，也适合激烈的在线对战。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2324150/extras/96bb90d19ccb488a84fcfad555de1c65.poster.avif?t=1770800965\" width=614 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2324150/extras/96bb90d19ccb488a84fcfad555de1c65.webm?t=1770800965\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2324150/extras/96bb90d19ccb488a84fcfad555de1c65.mp4?t=1770800965\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>游戏支持多达17种语言</strong>，包括波兰语、英语、德语、法语、日语、韩语和中文——让全球玩家都能轻松体验。<br><br>这是对以下玩家的必备推荐：<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>桌游和回合制游戏爱好者<br></li><li>重视深度战术与非对称派系的玩家<br></li><li>神经岛宇宙的粉丝——现在也可以在PC上体验</li></ul><br>",
    "supported_languages": "英语, 法语, 意大利语, 德语, 西班牙语 - 西班牙, 波兰语, 葡萄牙语 - 巴西, 俄语, 土耳其语, 捷克语, 日语, 韩语, 罗马尼亚语, 匈牙利语, 乌克兰语",
